{"tid":2094421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁愛詩：國安法可更好懲治本土恐怖襲擊","createTime":"2020-07-04T15:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T04:18:30.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ed73e4e39a070c6650e2504ef7ad5b574ef9f2f8","tid":2094421,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T15:25:05.000Z","msg":"基本法委員會前副主任梁愛詩說，港區國安法兼顧內地與香港法律制度的差異，尊重和保障香港市民的合法權益，懲治危害國家安全的犯罪分子，將推動香港恢復安寧，並為解決香港其他深層次問題創造良好的外部環境。<br />\n<br />\n梁愛詩接受新華社訪問時說，本港過去對於分裂國家、顛覆國家政權、勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全罪，缺乏法律手段進行懲治，對恐怖活動罪，香港法律側重於打擊國際恐怖分子在香港實施恐怖襲擊，對本土恐怖襲擊的打擊力度不夠。香港國安法實施，會使特區政府相關部門有法可依，更好地懲治有關罪行。"},{"pid":"b51dde3f87c40def5936bf76b2ad170aeff7beb2","tid":2094421,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T15:25:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1329070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1329070&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmsjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=fde7a2b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1329070</a>"},{"pid":"48d98ff02b416612b78ce677fad3952bb25c8aef","tid":2094421,"uid":82938,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T15:26:04.000Z","msg":"同新疆條路一樣"},{"pid":"d82e6ca6459b0963cf06e6b687f89405cffe99e4","tid":2094421,"uid":19527,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"721恐怖襲襲懲治左未"},{"pid":"a234e51ed920a0f7249a886178c5abcc0149b272","tid":2094421,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T15:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2906690/org/65278f6b98b421d06eaec8d484f6cfdd.jpg/kqqJ8tDFCzQRQIAkkKgs9xGb3F5IczO_GEZdWRhGXVk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2906690%2Forg%2F65278f6b98b421d06eaec8d484f6cfdd.jpg%2FkqqJ8tDFCzQRQIAkkKgs9x